@baseUrl = http://localhost:5001/api

### Create a Task
POST {{baseUrl}}/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Learn Mongoose CRUD",
    "description": "Implement Create, Read, Update, and Delete operations using Mongoose and Express."
}

### Get All Tasks
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks

### Get Single Task (Replace ID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks/<TASK_ID>

### Update a Task (Replace ID)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/tasks/<TASK_ID>
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "completed": true
}

### Delete a Task (Replace ID)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/tasks/<TASK_ID>
